{"tid":2099731,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突發】日官房長官菅義偉　接受自民黨小組對華譴責決議　習近平訪日或取消","createTime":"2020-07-08T12:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T15:42:17.000Z","uid":97944,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d7e2667cb91fb3094e9a75b2d6e5f208860bc8de","tid":2099731,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T12:50:48.000Z","msg":"香港實施國安法，引發國際社會關注，日本執政自民黨早前通過譴責決議，要求取消中國國家主席訪日行程，據《共同社》報道，自民黨外交小組組長中山泰秀今日和官房長官菅義偉會面，菅義偉接受了對華譴責協議，將切實認真對待。<br />\n<br />\n但報道又指，目前交予菅義偉的決議，雖然表明對中國訂立國安法予以「強烈譴責」，但由於黨內外壓力，包括親華派幹事長二階俊博等提出異議，決議由原草案「請求取消」習近平訪問，改為外交小組「不得不請求取消」，亦列明是「小組決議」，而不是自民黨「全黨」。"},{"pid":"6a4edcfc6bdc3cacd0de44ecfba01e8a78fdd20e","tid":2099731,"uid":97944,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T12:51:05.000Z","msg":"Source:  立場<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%97%A5%E5%AE%98%E6%88%BF%E9%95%B7%E5%AE%98%E8%8F%85%E7%BE%A9%E5%81%89-%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E8%87%AA%E6%B0%91%E9%BB%A8%E5%B0%8F%E7%B5%84%E5%B0%8D%E8%8F%AF%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E6%B1%BA%E8%AD%B0-%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E8%A8%AA%E6%97%A5%E6%88%96%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88/?fbclid=IwAR2MGgIZ7MCJ-U4NN7hych8jHgMYnpjsnMd4ifO7u85KoN_BMi41j7x3WwM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2588%25BF%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25AE%2598%25E8%258F%2585%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%2581%2589-%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%258F%2597%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%25B5%2584%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%258F%25AF%25E8%25AD%25B4%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B6%2588%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2MGgIZ7MCJ-U4NN7hych8jHgMYnpjsnMd4ifO7u85KoN_BMi41j7x3WwM&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK2vf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=642b9772\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2588%